# Regenerate with: vhs docs/demo/demo.tape
# (run from the repo root; requires https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs)

Output docs/demo/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000
Set Height 560
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Hide
Type "clear && bash docs/demo/run.sh"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Sleep 1.5s
Type "?"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s
Type "9f2c8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d0e1f2a3b"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s
